{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":86,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_ping_qiu_jun","speaker_name":"平丘君","listener":"char_ji_qie","text":"你的身材愈来愈丰满，难怪昨晚大王都目不转睛地打量你。","tone":"调侃","chapter":237,"line_start":16,"line_end":18},{"speaker":"char_ji_qie","speaker_name":"姬妾","listener":"char_ping_qiu_jun","text":"若君上你把人家送给大王，奴家情愿自尽好了。","tone":"恳求","chapter":237,"line_start":20,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_ji_qie","speaker_name":"姬妾","listener":"char_ping_qiu_jun","text":"君上不是得去赴晚宴吗？竟偏要在这时刻逗人家。","tone":"调侃","chapter":237,"line_start":28,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_ping_qiu_jun","speaker_name":"平丘君","listener":"char_ji_qie","text":"现在满城风雨，什么大宴小宴都给项少龙闹得取消了。大王有令，凡窝藏项少龙或知情不报者，均要抄家灭族，哈！没有一条死尸比项少龙更值钱了，只尸首就可得赏五百块金子，累得人人在找寻这家伙。","tone":"陈述","chapter":237,"line_start":38,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_ji_qie","speaker_name":"姬妾","listener":"char_ping_qiu_jun","text":"奴家看他早已离城远去，否则为何整个大梁给翻转过来，仍找不到他半根寒毛？","tone":"疑问","chapter":237,"line_start":46,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_ji_qie","speaker_name":"姬妾","listener":"char_ping_qiu_jun","text":"这人真了得，要来便来，要去便去，谁都莫奈他何。","tone":"无奈","chapter":237,"line_start":50,"line_end":50},{"speaker":"char_ping_qiu_jun","speaker_name":"平丘君","listener":"char_ji_qie","text":"他走得轻松容易，却累死城守范大人，这趟抓不到项少龙，所有罪责都落到他的身上去。刚才他还来央我向大王说情，现在大王在气头上，我才不会笨得为他惹祸上身。","tone":"无奈","chapter":237,"line_start":52,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_ping_qiu_jun","speaker_name":"平丘君","listener":"char_ji_qie","text":"项少龙来得真不是时候，害我错失欣赏凤菲精彩表演的机会，明天她便要起程到齐国去，不知何时才会回来。我明天定要去送行。","tone":"无奈","chapter":237,"line_start":58,"line_end":60}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","name":"项少龙","alias":[],"identity":"穿越者/战国纵横家","faction":"无","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"穿越至战国的现代特种兵，身手了得，智勇双全","personality":{"traits":["机智","果断","机敏","坚韧","重情义"],"speech_style":"沉稳老练","temperament":"冷静"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[237],"source_refs":[{"chapter":237,"line_start":2,"line_end":3,"text":"项少龙睁开眼来，眼前仍是漆黑一片"}]},{"id":"char_ping_qiu_jun","name":"平丘君","alias":[],"identity":"魏国贵族","faction":"魏国","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"信陵君故宅现主人，与姬妾厮混的魏国贵族","personality":{"traits":["好色","圆滑","谨慎","享乐","精明"],"speech_style":"轻浮随意","temperament":"安逸"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[237],"source_refs":[{"chapter":237,"line_start":16,"line_end":18,"text":"只听一阵男声淫笑道"}]},{"id":"char_ji_qie","name":"姬妾","alias":[],"identity":"平丘君侍妾","faction":"魏国","role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"平丘君身边善解人意的侍妾","personality":{"traits":["妩媚","聪慧","善解人意","娇柔","机灵"],"speech_style":"撒娇娇嗔","temperament":"温柔"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[237],"source_refs":[{"chapter":237,"line_start":20,"line_end":22,"text":"一名女子的声音不依道"}]},{"id":"char_feng_fei","name":"凤菲","alias":["三大名姬之首"],"identity":"战国名姬","faction":"齐国","role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"三大名姬之首，风格独特的美女，即将前往齐国","personality":{"traits":["才华横溢","风格独特","高贵","神秘","优雅"],"speech_style":"优雅端庄","temperament":"从容"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[237],"source_refs":[{"chapter":237,"line_start":58,"line_end":60,"text":"害我错失欣赏凤菲精彩表演的机会"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_wei_guo","name":"魏国","type":"帮派","location":"大梁","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"战国七雄之一，都城大梁","source_refs":[{"chapter":237,"line_start":1,"line_end":5,"text":"大梁城中搜捕项少龙"}]}],"locations":[{"id":"loc_xin_ling_jun_gu_zhai","name":"信陵君故宅","region":"大梁","one_line":"信陵君旧居，现为平丘君所有，地下有密道","source_refs":[{"chapter":237,"line_start":8,"line_end":8,"text":"铜管赫然入目"}]}],"items":[{"id":"item_tong_guan","name":"铜管","type":"special","owner":"char_ping_qiu_jun","one_line":"装在密室入口侧的监听铜管","description":"安装在密室入口侧的铜管，既可监听密室动静，也可将上面声息传下来，闪闪生辉","effects":["监听"],"origin":"信陵君故宅","rarity":"寻常凡品","related_characters":["char_xiang_shao_long"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[237],"source_refs":[{"chapter":237,"line_start":10,"line_end":12,"text":"铜管赫然入目，它被装在入口侧，闪闪生辉"}]}]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":87,"line_end":160,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_fan_jiang_jun","speaker_name":"范将军","listener":"char_ping_qiu_jun","text":"这次我们来找平丘君，是为了搜捕项少龙的事。","tone":"陈述","chapter":237,"line_start":106,"line_end":108},{"speaker":"char_ping_qiu_jun","speaker_name":"平丘君","listener":"char_fan_jiang_jun","text":"范将军找项少龙，为何竟会找到我这里来呢？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":237,"line_start":112,"line_end":112},{"speaker":"char_long_yang_jun","speaker_name":"龙阳君","listener":"char_fan_jiang_jun","text":"范将军敢以人头担保，项少龙仍未离城，假如他仍躲在城内，那最有可能是藏在这里了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":237,"line_start":122,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_ping_qiu_jun","speaker_name":"平丘君","listener":"char_long_yang_jun","text":"没有可能的。我曾着人把府内每寸的地方都彻底搜查过，若他在这里，绝瞒不过我们，更瞒不过狗儿灵敏的鼻子。","tone":"焦急","chapter":237,"line_start":128,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_fan_jiang_jun","speaker_name":"范将军","listener":"char_ping_qiu_jun","text":"我们问过信陵君以前的手下，证实项少龙当日该是由地道一类的通道逃出这里，不过却没人知道地道的出入口在何处。","tone":"陈述","chapter":237,"line_start":132,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_long_yang_jun","speaker_name":"龙阳君","listener":"char_ping_qiu_jun","text":"平丘君可询问府内各人，看看有没有忽然少了食物、衣服一类的事，便可知项少龙是否藏在下面的地道。","tone":"冷静","chapter":237,"line_start":136,"line_end":138}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_long_yang_jun","name":"龙阳君","alias":[],"identity":"魏国权臣","faction":"魏国","role":"npc","archetype":"scholar","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"魏国权臣，与项少龙有旧交，奉命搜捕却内心挣扎","personality":{"traits":["精明","矛盾","重情义","憔悴","谨慎"],"speech_style":"沉稳低沉","temperament":"忧虑"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"宿敌","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"旧识被迫对立"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[237],"source_refs":[{"chapter":237,"line_start":104,"line_end":104,"text":"龙阳君，他脸色苍白，骤然间似若老了几年的样子"}]},{"id":"char_fan_jiang_jun","name":"范将军","alias":["城守范大人"],"identity":"大梁城守","faction":"魏国","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"大梁城守，负责搜捕项少龙，压力巨大","personality":{"traits":["刚毅","尽责","焦虑","果断","务实"],"speech_style":"严肃正式","temperament":"紧张"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[237],"source_refs":[{"chapter":237,"line_start":106,"line_end":108,"text":"那将军首先发言道"}]}],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_long_yang_jun","updates":{"rank":"出神入化","source_refs":[{"chapter":237,"line_start":122,"line_end":124,"text":"龙阳君叹道"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"宿敌","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"旧识被迫对立"}]}]}
